# Branvia Project Structure Guide

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 15 with App Router
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Database:** PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Authentication:** Better Auth (email/password + Google OAuth)
- **Styling:** CSS Modules
- **UI:** Lucide React icons, Framer Motion animations

## Key Files & Directories

### App Router Structure
- Main layout: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with auth & navigation
- Homepage: [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Main landing page
- Legal pages: [src/app/(legal)/](mdc:src/app/(legal)/) - Contact, privacy, terms, etc.
- Auth API: [src/app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts](mdc:src/app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts)
- Prompt cards: [src/app/prompt-card/[id]/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/prompt-card/[id]/page.tsx)

### Components Organization
- **Main sections:** [src/_components/main/](mdc:src/_components/main/) - Page-specific components
  - [HeroSection/](mdc:src/_components/main/HeroSection/) - Landing hero with stats
  - [PromptGallery/](mdc:src/_components/main/PromptGallery/) - AI platform showcase + image grid
  - [AboutSection/](mdc:src/_components/main/AboutSection/) - About content
  - [PricingSection/](mdc:src/_components/main/PricingSection/) - Pricing plans
  - [FooterSection/](mdc:src/_components/main/FooterSection/) - Footer
- **UI components:** [src/_components/ui/](mdc:src/_components/ui/) - Reusable components
  - [Navbar/](mdc:src/_components/ui/Navbar/) - Navigation
  - [WordsPullUp.tsx](mdc:src/_components/ui/WordsPullUp.tsx) - Animated text component

### Core Libraries
- **Authentication:** [src/_lib/_auth/](mdc:src/_lib/_auth/) - Better Auth setup
- **Database:** [src/_lib/_db/](mdc:src/_lib/_db/) - Prisma client
- **Providers:** [src/_lib/_providers/](mdc:src/_lib/_providers/) - React context providers

### Configuration
- Package config: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
- Database schema: [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
- Next.js config: [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js)
- Docker setup: [compose.dev.yaml](mdc:compose.dev.yaml)

## Business Context
This is an AI product image generation platform for small brands. Users can generate professional product images or use prompts on their preferred AI platforms (DALL-E, Midjourney, etc.).
